    "description": "想创造出梦想中的卧室吗？在《我的梦想卧室》中，你可以实现任何想法，任何颜色搭配，没有预算限制。你拥有创造一切的自由。<br><br>《我的梦想卧室》是一款关于创造梦寐以求的卧室的模拟建造游戏。游戏提供琳琅满目的家具、电脑及其配件、海报、画作、植物和其他室内装饰细节等着你去使用。试试每个物品，并布置你梦想中的卧室。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2200780/extras/c63b630c6ec51e7e0eeb2b6558ecdef6.avif?t=1770404871\" width=620 height=78 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2200780/extras/f71e6051b46e9aec9da539f3227e8796.poster.avif?t=1770404871\" width=620 height=349 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2200780/extras/f71e6051b46e9aec9da539f3227e8796.webm?t=1770404871\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>依照自己的想法放置家具。没有网格的限制，完全自由摆放。如果你对家具摆放的位置不满意可以随时移动到新位置。房间里的家具没有数量限制。创造出一个又小又整洁的办公室还是一个摆满电脑和其他物品的大工作室，都取决于你。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2200780/extras/c11a8923b64b34d1d541369871c024ad.avif?t=1770404871\" width=620 height=81 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2200780/extras/8dff016ece239516f0c7767ec4acb105.poster.avif?t=1770404871\" width=620 height=349 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2200780/extras/8dff016ece239516f0c7767ec4acb105.webm?t=1770404871\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>改变家具的颜色。RGB色域里所有的颜色都可以使用。每个家具都可以单独定制颜色。这可以让你创造出各种颜色搭配，还能改变几乎所有物品的颜色，包括：门、窗户、家具、背景。尝试组合不同的颜色和色调来创造出你认为最好看的房间！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2200780/extras/c86e90c86a78b3742e0ddaef808224e1.avif?t=1770404871\" width=620 height=81 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2200780/extras/b5127b6a815af5dab33f66640fa4693b.poster.avif?t=1770404871\" width=620 height=349 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2200780/extras/b5127b6a815af5dab33f66640fa4693b.webm?t=1770404871\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>海量壁纸和墙漆等着你去使用。想在房间里贴上鲜花壁纸吗？或者喜欢loft风格并且想要一堵砖墙？单独粉刷每面墙来创造出最出人意料的墙面风格，或点击一下粉刷整个房间，让想象力尽情发挥。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2200780/extras/f07496972c973410719623c0c2529de5.avif?t=1770404871\" width=620 height=81 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2200780/extras/b2c8fadf4d6eaa0f11908bf5566a5a80.poster.avif?t=1770404871\" width=620 height=349 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2200780/extras/b2c8fadf4d6eaa0f11908bf5566a5a80.webm?t=1770404871\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>在不同天气和光照条件下查看卧室。我们提供了五种天气选择：晴天、日落、雨天、雪天和夜晚。每个选项都会给卧室带来不一样的氛围，也让窗外的景色焕然一新。在雨雪天气下，窗户上会出现雨雪，沉浸感十足。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2200780/extras/315429f9c196d91571fa394657a1fda9.avif?t=1770404871\" width=620 height=81 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2200780/extras/20876da4b5740e2a3339e74427b73b29.poster.avif?t=1770404871\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2200780/extras/20876da4b5740e2a3339e74427b73b29.webm?t=1770404871\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2200780/extras/20876da4b5740e2a3339e74427b73b29.mp4?t=1770404871\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在《我的梦想卧室》里，你可以随意调整卧室的大小和布局。在蓝图模式里设置墙壁，放置窗户、门。在任何时间改变卧室的大小和布局，在布置卧室的过程中也可以！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特点</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 放松、沉浸、多样化的游玩体验，限制你的只有想象力<br></li><li> 种类繁多的家具家具、电脑及其配件、海报、画作、植物和其他室内装饰细节等着你去布置卧室。<br></li><li> 放松减压的游戏氛围<br></li><li> RGB灯光<br></li><li>Steam Workshop</li></ul>",
